Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:56.02,IN-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\an8}敵人在等著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:02.25,IN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\an8}君にも待ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:02.25,IN-TC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\an8}也在等著你
